Hello,

I downloaded the CVS-Version today and did not like the sliders in the 
GUI, so here is a fix ;-D

diff notebook.c notebook.c_old
404c404
<                                               
100.0/(double)currentMaximum);
---
 >                                               
10.0*100.0/(double)currentMaximum);
408c408
<                               g_signal_connect_after(G_OBJECT(widget), 
"change-value", G_CALLBACK(range_callback), NULL);
---
 >                               
g_signal_connect_after(G_OBJECT(widget), "value-changed", 
G_CALLBACK(range_callback), NULL);


It works for me..

Regards
-Ulrich


